<http://dx.doi.org/10.26107/RBZ-2021-0068>
    bibo:endPage "521" ;
    bibo:journal "Raffles Bulletin of Zoology" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2021-12-03" ;
    bibo:startPage "507" ;
    bibo:volume "69" ;
    dc:creator "Tran, A. D.; Zettel, H." ;
    dc:date "2021" ;
    dc:title "Taxonomy of the Ranatra biroi group sensu Lansbury, 1972 (Nepomorpha: Nepidae), with descriptions of two new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7174621>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7174623>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7174627>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7174625> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7174621>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Parameres of Ranatra species. A, Ranatra digitata, from Sri Lanka (ZRC_ENT00013064); B, R. biroi, from Irian Jaya, Indonesia; C, R. rafflesi, holotype; D, R. rafflesi, from West Kalimantan, intermediate form (ZRC_ENT00013018); E,R.rafflesi, from West Kalimantan, slender form (ZRC_ENT00013054). C, D, E same scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7174621/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7174623>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Ranatra luzonensis, new species, male holotype. A, habitus; B, head, prothorax, and fore legs, dorsal view; C, head and prothorax, lateral view; D, antenna; E, metasternum; F, operculum; G, left paramere, lateral view. B, C same scale; E, F same scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7174623/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7174627>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Parameres of Ranatra species. A, R. longipes longipes, from Brunei; B, R. cardamomensis, from Natuna Island (ZRC_ ENT00013061); C, R. cardamomensis, from southern Thailand (ZRC_ENT00013063). B, C same scale. Note that the paramere hook of the Thai specimen (Fig. 4C) recurved further after being dry-mounted from an alcohol-preserved specimen; while still in alcohol, the apex was same as that in the type specimens." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7174627/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7174625>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Ranatra palawanensis, new species, male paratype. A, habitus; B, head, prothorax, and fore legs, dorsal view; C, head and prothorax, lateral view; D, antenna; E, metasternum; F, left paramere, lateral view. B, C same scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7174625/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

